      <title>日元波动有可能破坏今年最好的交易之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/japan-intervention-risks-derailing-emerging-market-carry-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本威胁要破坏今年最赚钱的货币押注之一：借入日元投资新兴市场货币的套利交易。]]></description>
